## Remarks  

> [!NOTE]
>  [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/includes/deprecatedcontent-md.md)]  

 <span data-ttu-id="2fb53-102"><xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity> Umożliwia ustawianie stanu aplikacji hosta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fb53-102">The <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity> allows for setting the state from the host application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2fb53-103">Dzięki temu aplikacja hosta zastąpić bieżący stan komputera stanu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fb53-103">This enables the host application to override the current state of a state machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2fb53-104">Można to osiągnąć enqueuing wystąpienia <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.SetStateEventArgs> klasy WorkflowQueue o nazwie stała <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity.SetStateQueueName?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fb53-104">This can be accomplished by enqueuing an instance of the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.SetStateEventArgs> class to the WorkflowQueue named by the constant <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity.SetStateQueueName?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="2fb53-105">Prostszy sposób, w tym celu jest użycie <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance.SetState%2A> metoda <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance> klasy.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fb53-105">A simpler way to accomplish this is to use the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance.SetState%2A> method in the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance> class.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="2fb53-106">Można użyć <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance.SetState%2A> metodę, aby wykonać operację metoda SetState z hosta, lub zrobić to samodzielnie przez enqueuing zdarzenie, aby przepływ pracy automatu stanów jak pokazano w poniższym przykładzie.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fb53-106">You can use the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance.SetState%2A> method to perform a SetState operation from the host, or you can do it yourself by enqueuing an event to the state machine workflow as shown in the following example.</span></span>  

```  
public void SetState(string targetStateName)  
{  
      if (targetStateName == null)  
      {  
            throw new ArgumentNullException("targetStateName");  
      }  
      SetStateEventArgs args1 = new SetStateEventArgs(targetStateName);  
      this.WorkflowInstance.EnqueueItemOnIdle("SetStateQueue", args1, null, null);  
}  
```  

 <span data-ttu-id="2fb53-107">Przepływ pracy automatu stanów używa specjalnych kolejki o nazwie `SetStateQueue` do nasłuchiwania na te zdarzenia specjalnych.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2fb53-107">The state machine workflow uses a special queue called `SetStateQueue` to listen to these special events.</span></span>
